oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jean Shepard and Tommy Cash at Camden Park
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Shepard, Jean, 1933-; Cash, Tommy; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing Jean Shepard and the Second Fiddles at Camden Park in Huntington, West Virginia on May 26 and Tommy Cash and the Tom Cats at Camden Park in Huntington, West Virginia on May 27. Poster features metal photoplates of Jean Shepard and Tommy Cash.
